{"tid":2240082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒人試過同好朋友創業？","createTime":"2020-10-12T11:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T04:01:04.000Z","uid":124400,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b911210bae5f05a6282bb6807035564b79f5a65f","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"小弟而家就經歷緊呢樣野，發現真係好難做落去<br />\n<br />\n事源我地開左間公司寫 App 俾人用，開發方面基本上我負責灑，咁我朋友就負責 marketing / social media / 拎 funding / 搞下手續之類。頭幾個月因為我要搞個 App，就叫佢寫定 proposal 準備去見投資人啦，但之後發現份野做完出嚟好多錯字 + 句子唔通順 + 睇完都唔明，我每次睇完都會留 comment 俾佢，建議佢改正，但係次次改完都係咁上下，到最後都係我自己重新做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，個 App 出世了，我就叫佢上 social media po 下野 / 落下廣告啦。雖然大家都唔係設計出身，但係佢 D 文案完全唔掂，先唔好講 顏色 / 內容 呢種主觀問題，佢連 置中 / 對齊 都唔知，圖片同文字好似打風咁，同佢講左好多次，但都係咁。大家睇到呢度，可能覺得佢做野好 hea，但係我相信佢儘左力，因為有時真係改左好多次，但都係不斷重覆同一個問題。<br />\n<br />\n另一問題係佢對自己作品有一定信心，佢覺得自己已經做得好好，所以有時講多兩句就會炆。當然我可以嘗試俾佢自由發揮（我一開始係咁）但係有時又過唔到自己，我又無理由次次幫佢執\b <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地十幾年朋友，而家拆伙佢就會覺得我飛起佢。雖然個 App 我用左好多時間心機做，但最壞打算可能係摺左間公司，大家如果係我會點做？<br />\n<br />\n(因為呢個係感情問題，所以就 Po 係感情台)"},{"pid":"2b9ce812a3db5d953099a1698405a947a4581fc3","tid":2240082,"uid":162421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"圖定老母"},{"pid":"fd47051914c9000f6cb47aa25e47ebb03bc96e90","tid":2240082,"uid":185238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"提提你，顏色唔係主觀問題，係有科學根據，可以學下"},{"pid":"af5f4b71a372e6d5ca3426de2fc4c3a25cd19616","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b9ce812a3db5d953099a1698405a947a4581fc3","tid":2240082,"uid":162421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"圖定老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Coevrg5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoevrg5.gif&h=89c28fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf0750940f00efc732e669881155fa570243963b","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd47051914c9000f6cb47aa25e47ebb03bc96e90","tid":2240082,"uid":185238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"提提你，顏色唔係主觀問題，係有科學根據，可以學下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"Thx bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43134355b0aa8204c544fe405a4af98ef20b2f3d","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"小弟而家煩惱緊點樣同時做到 尊重別人的工作 + 做好件事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f14658d72f44aa886f5ae2fbaeb5308c84d09e1","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"可能對方係好朋友，有時話完佢，我個心都會痛一痛，接受自己問題難，但原來要指出其他人問題都好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ebeac09a822557d585a8fa108dced0c9aca24b","tid":2240082,"uid":258374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"係咪你控制慾過強? <br />\n<br />\n你post D 內容上黎，俾大家過過眼，先有得評論<br />\n兩條友，而家口同鼻拗，<br />\n人地專做marketing ，你都唔信佢既能力，咪搵過個囉<br />\n求財姐"},{"pid":"e6a84f1aac1687c1bee8cfe49b3927b22df2fffb","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ebeac09a822557d585a8fa108dced0c9aca24b","tid":2240082,"uid":258374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"係咪你控制慾過強? <br />\n<br />\n你post D 內容上黎，俾大家過過眼，先有得評論<br />\n兩條友，而家口同鼻拗，<br />\n人地專做marketing ，你都唔信佢既能力，咪搵過個囉<br />\n求財姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"Thx Bro，內容我就唔方便 Po 啦。但關於控制慾，我有諗過呢個問題，所以都有搵過唔少朋友過目，佢地評價都係差唔多。一開始我都當睇唔到，有 D 朋友甚至走嚟問我：喂，張圖你整架？我都唔識點答"},{"pid":"99898ccad6ae89386ae267283972fd2f526310f6","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"純粹發下窂騷，我都係乖乖同佢坐低傾下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204d1cb49ec88a4e825d06127ec42e615b858c7c","tid":2240082,"uid":300630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"同朋友創業好on9"},{"pid":"8922a88f7bd89adc23afaaf80e3da9592e9eccd6","tid":2240082,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"可能係你有問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b1d9639609d6a7081bf2910b3cc86fcafff770","tid":2240082,"uid":124400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8922a88f7bd89adc23afaaf80e3da9592e9eccd6","tid":2240082,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"可能係你有問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"可能啦，有時語氣又重左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb762c7a50e1c19e5b625d8a63eae0e5a589c96","tid":2240082,"uid":84415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"簡單D講,你可以冇左佢,佢唔可以冇左你"},{"pid":"4597a659ea7d9f11f1dac8096244459c7be75f81","tid":2240082,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"試過 最後無朋友做"},{"pid":"d29e48d21ba17067142c1679840d643284a899d2","tid":2240082,"uid":86457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"中學做project都知其他人係靠唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更唔好講做生意<br />\n如果大家都係自己專業範疇就okay<br />\n但佢又唔係設計底<br />\n又走去做social media <br />\n姐係求其搵個人做都得<br />\n咁唔一定要係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}